Subject: [PATCH 1/2] feat: add Nerve Dark & Nerve Light themes (Vective brand)

- Add nerve-dark theme: Slate Deep backgrounds (#0F172A), Authority Cyan
  accent (#0891B2), Brand Cyan highlights (#22D3EE), Life Emerald success (#059669)
- Add nerve-light theme: White/Slate Wash surfaces, Authority Cyan accent,
  Vective brand surface palette
- Both themes placed first in theme selector for prominence
- Default theme changed from ayu-dark to nerve-dark
- All colors sourced from vectiveai.com/brand canonical palette
- Chart colors use Vective brand spectrum
